sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Session as Session workspace
    participant SBT as SBT/chiseltest
    participant Test as LivePipelineTest
    participant Bridge as ChiselBridge
    participant WS as Socket.IO

    User->>Browser: Select project src folder
    Browser->>API: POST /upload_and_detect (source map)
    API->>API: Filter paths and detect level
    API-->>Browser: Accepted sources, level, system BinaryFile
    User->>Browser: Select test and Compile & Simulate
    Browser->>WS: Join session room
    Browser->>API: POST /compile
    API->>Session: Copy scaffold, write Scala and BinaryFile
    API->>SBT: Launch controlled live test suite
    SBT->>Test: Elaborate and run Chisel tests
    Test->>Test: Generate VCD (headless test)
    Test-->>Bridge: Open session-specific TCP server
    Bridge->>Test: Connect, consume initial snapshot, reset
    Test-->>Bridge: Cycle-0 JSON snapshot
    Bridge-->>API: Initial processor state
    API-->>Browser: Compilation succeeded
    Browser->>WS: init / step command
    WS->>Bridge: step
    Bridge->>Test: "step" line
    Test->>Test: Advance clock one cycle
    Test-->>Bridge: JSON snapshot
    Bridge->>API: Raw snapshot
    API->>API: Decode instructions and append history
    API->>WS: Processed update + cycle log
    WS-->>Browser: Session-room event
    Browser->>Browser: Update SVG, registers, and console
